{"tid":1991088,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公開大學調查35%港人重用口罩 一罩用足兩日半","createTime":"2020-04-27T07:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T08:20:55.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"999ca1804a0ca33b85d94467ac88810b67fd1e75","tid":1991088,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T07:54:10.000Z","msg":"口罩在疫情下供不應求升價十倍。公開大學一項調查發現，三成半港人會重用口罩，平均兩日半更換一個。<br />\n<br />\n公開大學護理及健康學院署理院長李燕瓊率領12人學生團隊，本月以電話訪問1000名香港成年人使用口罩的習慣。結果發現，345名受訪者（34.5%）有重用口罩習慣，平均每個口罩用2.5天；當中115人（11.5%）有消毒口罩。結果同時發現，60歲或以上群組，明顯較年輕組別較常重用口罩。<br />\n<br />\n團隊推算，全港約三分一成年人在疫情期間都「舊罩重用」，情況不理想。李燕瓊相信市民重用口罩，並非因為實際擁有的口罩不夠用，而是擔心將來不夠用。<br />\n<br />\n醫學會副會長兼家庭醫生鄭志文提醒市民，口罩是否有效，並非以使用時數或日數計算，而是視乎口罩質地、在甚麼環境下使用及儲存方法是否妥當等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/MW2DenOMWAQ95wmqUmREmA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzQ3O2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20200427a150528.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FMW2DenOMWAQ95wmqUmREmA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzQ3O2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20200427a150528.jpg&h=c91a7bf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%AC%E5%A4%A7%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A535-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E9%87%8D%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E7%BD%A9%E7%94%A8%E8%B6%B3%E5%85%A9%E6%97%A5%E5%8D%8A-070400483.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A535-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E7%2594%25A8%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%258D%258A-070400483.html&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4UKa%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=66cef3f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%AC%E5%A4%A7%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A535-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E9%87%8D%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E7%BD%A9%E7%94%A8%E8%B6%B3%E5%85%A9%E6%97%A5%E5%8D%8A-070400483.html</a>"},{"pid":"ce6c32d49d75398ca5e743dcd820634ad63b7f00","tid":1991088,"uid":66242,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T07:56:21.000Z","msg":"醫學會副會長兼家庭醫生鄭志文提醒市民，口罩是否有效，並<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">非以使用時數或日數計算</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咁個標題做乜撚嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e0bf86909fcc7105230b619937f951f252a7b4","tid":1991088,"uid":201512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T08:05:59.000Z","msg":"三條女唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知除咗口罩點樣呢"},{"pid":"8ffa4b73edcf3a38bdcb2ce23f9eee9c333313bb","tid":1991088,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14e0bf86909fcc7105230b619937f951f252a7b4","tid":1991088,"uid":201512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T08:05:59.000Z","msg":"三條女唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知除咗口罩點樣呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T08:17:08.000Z","msg":"左邊似支那G"},{"pid":"b2bf75e01f77cf8c88cef3edc33b3d26501cf7dc","tid":1991088,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T08:18:09.000Z","msg":"奶罩用2日半真係唔岩既"},{"pid":"d6435ee0aa60428d2a8328ea9ea5b39daeaf3ca5","tid":1991088,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T08:20:55.000Z","msg":"我一個奶罩, 用接近一個月 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}